      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this superlative example of automotive engineering, preserved in a state that transcends the typical pre-owned market. This vehicle remains in impeccable showroom condition, exhibiting no discernible wear and reflecting a history of fastidious, climate-controlled preservation. Every surface and mechanical component has been rigorously vetted to ensure it meets our uncompromising criteria for aesthetic and functional perfection. For the discerning driver who demands nothing less than excellence, this represents a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle of investment-grade quality.",
      "price": 46500.0,
