    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. This car is in incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been pampered since day one, kept tucked away in a garage, and it drives like a total dream. You really have to see it in person to appreciate how spotless it is. If you're looking for something that's been cared for with a lot of love, this is definitely the one for you! Feel free to reach out with any questions at all!",
      "price": 43500.0,
