      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E92 M3, a definitive example of the high-revving S65 naturally aspirated V8. This specimen features a pristine 8,400 RPM redline and has undergone rigorous preventative maintenance, including documented rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service. The M-DCT dual-clutch transmission operates with surgical precision, paired with a factory-spec limited-slip differential for optimal power delivery. The chassis remains taut, supported by Electronic Damper Control (EDC) with no signs of bushing fatigue or subframe stress. Finished with impeccable paint depth and zero curb rash on the forged alloy wheels, this vehicle represents a turnkey opportunity for the purist collector seeking peak atmospheric performance.",
